trans-unit.source: Enables upgraded Visual Basic 6.0 <see langword="WebClass" /> projects to run in ASP.NET.
When a Visual Basic 6.0 `WebClass` project is upgraded to [!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)], it is converted to an [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] Web-site project.
trans-unit.target: 当 Visual Basic 6.0`WebClass`项目升级到[!INCLUDE[vbprvb](~/includes/vbprvb-md.md)]，它将转换为[!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)]网站项目。

trans-unit.source: Declarations are added to your project: one for the `WebClass` and one for each `WebItem` and `Template` in the `WebClass` project.
trans-unit.target: 声明添加到你的项目： 一个用于`WebClass`，另一个用于每个`WebItem`和`Template`中`WebClass`项目。

trans-unit.source: A `Page_Load` event procedure is added to the project.

This creates first a `WebClass` object and then <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebItem> objects for each `WebItem` and `Template` associated with the Visual Basic 6.0 `WebClass` project.
trans-unit.target: 这将首先创建`WebClass`对象，然后<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebItem>每个对象`WebItem`和`Template`与 Visual Basic 6.0`WebClass`项目。

trans-unit.source: Finally, in the `Page_Load` event procedure, you will see a call to the `WebClass` Compatibility runtime: <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebClass.ProcessEvents%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 最后，在`Page_Load`事件过程中，你将看到调用`WebClass`兼容性运行时： <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebClass.ProcessEvents%2A>。

trans-unit.source: This enables the runtime to render the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebItem> specified in the Request URL.
trans-unit.target: 这使运行时能够呈现<xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebItem>在请求 URL 中指定。

trans-unit.source: This code is the only new code added to your upgraded project and serves only to emulate the underlying behavior of the Visual Basic 6.0 `WebClass` runtime.
trans-unit.target: 此代码是仅新的代码添加到升级后的项目，仅用于模拟的 Visual Basic 6.0 基础行为`WebClass`运行时。
